   <a name="computer" class="anchor"></a>
   <h2>Software for Your Computer</h2>
   <div class="main_section">
      <div class="row">
         <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-6">
            <p>
               Use our free software for your laptop or desktop comptuer to configure your Speck and optionally set it
               up to upload its data to your account on specksensor.com. Alternatively, you can use the Speck software
               to download the data directly to your computer.
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin:50px 0">
               <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/speck/anchbeboblnigmihhclbdkpdglecnimi" role="button" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-download"></i> Download</a>
            </p>
            <p class="fine_print">
               The Speck app is available for free on the Chrome Web Store. The Speck app requires that you have
               the Google Chrome web browser installed on either Windows 7+ or Mac OS 10.8+.
            </p>
         </div>
         <div id="screenshot" class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 hidden-xs img-responsive">
            <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/speck/anchbeboblnigmihhclbdkpdglecnimi" target="chrome_app"><img src="/images/speck_app_screenshot_no_shadow.png" alt="The Speck app" class="img-responsive"></a>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>

   <div class="main_section">
      <h3>Setup and Requirements</h3>
      <div>
         <p>
            You will need to have your Speck plugged in to your computer in order to use the Speck app. Simply use the
            USB cable supplied with your Speck&mdash;the small plug goes into the Speck, and the larger one goes into
            the USB port on your computer.
         </p>
         <p>
            You will also need to have the
            <a href="http://www.google.com/chrome/" target="get_chrome">Google Chrome web browser</a> installed on your
            computer. The Speck app is a Google Chrome app, and thus requires Google Chrome to be installed.
         </p>
      </div>
   </div>

   <div class="main_section">
      <h3>Download and Installation</h3>
      <div>
         <p>
            To install the software on your computer, go to the
            <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/speck/anchbeboblnigmihhclbdkpdglecnimi">Speck app's page on the Chrome Web Store</a>,
            and then click the "Add To Chrome" button. The videos below demonstrate the download and installation
            process in detail for Mac and Windows.
         </p>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
         <div class="col-xs-6">
            {{> vimeo_video_thumbnail_with_caption videoId="128538234" title="Installing the Speck App on a Mac" caption="Installing on a Mac" thumbnailImageFilename="519708010_640.jpg"}}
         </div>
         <div class="col-xs-6">
            {{> vimeo_video_thumbnail_with_caption videoId="128538327" title="Installing the Speck App on Windows" caption="Installing on Windows" thumbnailImageFilename="519708430_640.jpg"}}
